		<h2>Toast with Sliced Bananas and Nutella</h2>
		<img src="images/banana sandwhich.jpg" alt="Breakfast"/>
	    <!--- this image can be accessed at <a href="http://www.thecookingmom.com/cooking-community/member-recipes/nutella-and-banana-sandwich/http://www.thecookingmom.com/cooking-community/member-recipes/nutella-and-banana-sandwich/"--->
		<h3>Ingredients</h3>
		<ul>
		<li>2 slices of bread</li>
		<li>sliced banana</li>
		<li>Nutella</li>
		
		</ul>
		<h3>Method</h3>
		<ul>
		<li>Put bread in toaster</li>
		<li>slice up banana</li>
		<li>spread nutella on toast</li>
		<li>place slices of banana on toast</li>
		</ul>
		
