		<a name="lunch" id="lunch"></a>
		<h2>BBQ Chicken Sandwhich</h2>
		<img src="images/bbq.jpg" alt="Bbq chicken sandwhich"/>
		<!--- this image can be accessed at <a href="http://www.eatingwell.com/recipes/bbq_chicken_sandwich.htmlhttp://www.eatingwell.com/recipes/bbq_chicken_sandwich.html"--->
		<h2>Ingredients</h2>
		<ul>
		<li>1/2 cup shredded cooked chicken</li>
        <li>1/4 cup shredded carrots</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons barbecue sauce</li>
        <li>2 teaspoons light ranch dressing</li>
        <li>1 small whole-wheat sandwich bun</li>
        <li>1 leaf romaine lettuce</li>
		</ul>
		<h2>Method</h2>
		<ul>
		<li>Combine chicken </li>
        <li>carrots and barbecue sauce in a bowl. <li> 
		<li>Spread ranch dressing on the bun. <li>
		<li>Top with the chicken mixture and lettuce. <li>
		</ul>
		
